"Viki is a global TV site, where millions of people watch their favorite TV shows, movies, as well as curated lifestyle clips and original videos -- translated into 200+ languages by a community of avid fans. Viki’s publishing arm, Soompi, is the leader in online communities for K-pop and K-entertainment. Together, Soompi and Viki deliver fan-driven competitions, original videos and articles, music charts, and exclusive interviews with K-pop celebrities.
Together, we’re breaking down barriers that stand between great entertainment and its fans, no matter where they are!
https://www.viki.com"
